{"tid":1949051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日確診白警今朝有翻工!!!","createTime":"2020-03-29T11:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:45:32.000Z","uid":346581,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91e5e292cd134338e03c0b5c714ab099e7290a32","tid":1949051,"uid":346581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"唔驚! 相信政府!<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎在本港肆虐近3個月，確診個案突破600宗；過去10個月連番對市民施暴濫權、3萬人的香港警隊，截至周日（29日）亦增至3人染疫。據悉，初步確診的31歲何姓男警，駐守西九龍總部機動部隊，肺部有纖維化，發燒至38&deg;C，留醫明愛醫院，報稱與早前確診的22歲深水埗軍裝巡邏女警、第428號病人沒接觸。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君在記者會表示，暫未有相關個案資料。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該男警今日有上班，由於西九PTU現於警察遊樂會內戒備及到旺角警署換衫，故警隊內部已叫同事暫避免去遊樂會，相信該處需大清洗，而同該男警同team嘅40名伙計相信需要隔離。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Apple"},{"pid":"7ef29e70e850b300eaf217b6ab91c3ff4aec01fc","tid":1949051,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"要呃ot,病都唔抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24cb172c902af1f26eef23cd7f41696ab303eede","tid":1949051,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"白警(白肺)"},{"pid":"adb161f5bf88e6b3ac08d619de73de1351d8c71d","tid":1949051,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afdef6ef8a2ad520ba77c8aa619f77c498ac610","tid":1949051,"uid":75982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e641a67ef7fc58f99af6e993288bebe2609e1e81","tid":1949051,"uid":245292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s